page.title: 09HEALTH, KINGSBARNS
page.content: {WELFARE COMMITTEE} THERE IS A VOLUNTARY ORGANIZATION CALLED "THE KINGSBARNS' WELFARE COMMITTEE". ITS FUNCTION IS TO HELP THE SENIOR CITIZENS WHO FORM A QUARTER OF THE POPULATION. {HOUSING, KINGSBARNS} THERE ARE TWO TYPES: COUNCIL HOUSES AND PRIVATE HOUSES. MOST PRIVATE HOUSES ARE STONE BUILT. {LANDSCAPE, KINGSBARNS} GENERALLY FLAT, INTENSIVELY FARMED. MAINLY DECIDUOUS TREES. {BUILDINGS, KINGSBARNS THE CHURCH IS THE MAIN ARCHITECTURAL BUILDING. IT IS 358 YEARS OLD AND BUILT ON THE SITE OF A FORMER CHURCH.
